The paper deals with the learnability of logic programs, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The negative results presented in the paper involve cryptographic hardness, which falls under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the complexity of learning these programs, which could be considered a topic in computational complexity (cs.CC) and data structures (cs.DS).
